subproject.description: The key components of the project will include the establishment of TB/HIV joint Technical Coordinating Units in the MoH-GoSS, organise national level TB/HIV planning meetings to review and evaluate progress, establish an Advocacy, Communication and Social Mobilisation (ACSM) Unit, monitoring and evaluation of collaborative TB/HIV activities, increased TB case findings among PLWHA, provision of treatment for latent TB infection for HIV positive patients, and the provision of infection control services in health care settings and or congregate settings.
